modName: Improved Armor of the Old Gods
summary: A few tweaks to the Armor of the Old Gods, mostly the enchantments, to make it more worth using.
descriptionHtml: This mod boosts the enchantments of the Armor of the Old Gods given to you by Madinok (pretty sure I misspelled it) by siding with the forsworn in the Cidna Mine quest, and also (hopefully) boosts the armor rating to be better than elven gilded.
author: zinx43267
